{
  "texts": [
    "As explained earlier (§3.1), a naive low-rank multiplicative adaptation of W 0 has limitations.",
    "We present here the empirical verification of the same, and the results are shown in Table 6.",
    "The experiments were done on RoBERTa large on a subset of GLUE tasks, and all the hyperparameters and training conditions were kept exactly the same, apart from the presence and absence of the rank inflation strategies.",
    "The results for the I + have been reproduced for comparison.",
    "Further, we evaluate the effectiveness of the proposed rank inflation strategies by monitoring the rank of matrices throughout the training procedure."
  ]
}